OL,3,CNewcastle appoints first female
OL,4,Ccouncil leader in history
OL,6,FNewcastle has officially appointed the
OL,7,Ffirst female council leader in the
OL,8,Fcity's history.
OL,10,FKaren Kilgour was formally ratified as
OL,11,FNewcastle City Council's new Labour
OL,12,Fleader on Wednesday (2 October),
OL,13,Fhaving been chosen on Monday evening
OL,14,Fby her party as Nick Kemp's successor.
