OL,3,CNewcastle appoints first female
OL,4,Ccouncil leader in history
OL,6,FHe resigned last month after it
OL,7,Femerged that he was the subject of a
OL,8,Fbullying complaint from a senior
OL,9,Fcouncil officer, director of
OL,10,Finvestment and growth Michelle Percy,
OL,11,Fand has said that he strenuously
OL,12,Fdenies the accusation.
OL,14,FCllr Kilgour has served as Cllr Kemp's
OL,15,Fdeputy since 2022 and was previously
OL,16,Fsecond-in-command in the final year of
OL,17,FNick Forbes' administration.
