OL,3,CNewcastle appoints first female
OL,4,Ccouncil leader in history
OL,6,FFollowing a vote to confirm her
OL,7,Fascension to the leadership at
OL,8,FWednesday's full council meeting, the
OL,9,FWest Fenham ward councillor thanked
OL,10,FCllr Kemp and said she took "great
OL,11,Fpride" in being the first woman ever
OL,12,Fto hold the job.
OL,14,FThe Local Democracy Reporting Service
OL,15,Freports her immediate task will be to
OL,16,Fseek to provide stability at the civic
OL,17,Fcentre following a turbulent period
OL,18,Fand unite factions within a ruling
OL,19,FLabour group in which divisions have
OL,20,Fbeen obvious for several years.
