OL,3,CNewcastle appoints first female
OL,4,Ccouncil leader in history
OL,6,FShe said: "It is the honour of my life
OL,7,Fto be able to lead the city I love and
OL,8,Fstand up for the people who call
OL,9,FNewcastle home. I also want to take
OL,10,Fthis opportunity to thank Cllr Kemp
OL,11,Ffor all his hard work during his time
OL,12,Fas leader, and for the personal
OL,13,Fsupport he has shown to me. I know how
OL,14,Fmuch he cares about this city.
OL,26,@nD@KOU
