OL,3,CNewcastle appoints first female
OL,4,Ccouncil leader in history
OL,6,F"It gives me great pride to be the
OL,7,Ffirst woman to hold this important
OL,8,Fposition. Newcastle is a city that has
OL,9,Fcontinually shown that women can rise
OL,10,Fto the very top, holding a number of
OL,11,Fimportant roles across the public,
OL,12,Fprivate and community sectors.
OL,14,F"While we're fortunate to live in an
OL,15,Fincredibly forward-thinking and
OL,16,Finclusive city, I am determined to
OL,17,Fstand for all those who have
OL,18,Fpreviously been, and continue to be,
OL,19,Fmarginalised for characteristics
OL,20,Fbeyond their control.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
