OL,3,CNewcastle appoints first female
OL,4,Ccouncil leader in history
OL,6,F"It is an exciting time for Newcastle
OL,7,Fand the wider region, with the
OL,8,Fformation of the new North East
OL,9,FCombined Authority presenting
OL,10,Fopportunities for the North East to
OL,11,Fthrive."
OL,13,FEarlier in the meeting, she had been
OL,14,Fasked by Lib Dem opposition leader
OL,15,FColin Ferguson how the council would
OL,16,F"restore public confidence" after the
OL,17,Frecent controversy.
