OL,7,F"shown their confidence and their
OL,8,Ftrust" in Labour at the ballot box
OL,9,Fthis year and that her administration
OL,10,Fwould "very much focus on delivery" on
OL,11,Fkey issues including tackling poverty
OL,12,Fand helping people struggling with the
OL,13,Fcost of living.
