OL,3,CNewcastle appoints first female
OL,4,Ccouncil leader in history
OL,6,FThe city council is yet to confirm
OL,7,Fwhether a formal investigation will be
OL,8,Flaunched into the complaint made
OL,9,Fagainst Cllr Kemp, who continues to
OL,10,Fsit as a councillor for Byker, by Ms
OL,11,FPercy.
OL,13,FCllr Kilgour has sat on the council
OL,14,Fsince 2014 and has held responsibility
OL,15,Ffor issues including public health and
OL,16,Fadult social care during her time in
OL,17,Fthe authority's cabinet.
