OL,3,CNewcastle appoints first female
OL,4,Ccouncil leader in history
OL,6,FCllr Kemp led the authority since May
OL,7,F2022, after a dramatic end to Mr
OL,8,FForbes' long reign in the leadership
OL,9,Frole when he was deselected by Labour
OL,10,FParty members in his ward.
OL,12,FHe was challenged for the leadership
OL,13,Fin each of the past two years, most
OL,14,Frecently when he narrowly defeated Dan
OL,15,FGreenhough this May in a 23-21 vote.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, there have been multiple
OL,18,Fquestions raised about the culture
OL,19,Fbehind the scenes at the civic centre
OL,20,Fand within Newcastle Labour.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G12/13
