OL,6,FCouncil chief executive Pam Smith
OL,7,Frefused to deny the presence of a
OL,8,F"toxic" atmosphere and bullying in the
OL,9,Fadministration when she was questioned
OL,10,Fin front of the authority's audit
OL,11,Fcommittee last year, while multiple ex-
OL,12,FLabour councillors have cited alleged
OL,13,Fbullying within the party over the
OL,14,Flast 18 months.
